CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 21, 1961, pg. 29, reads: "Westinghouse Bulldogs - Members of the Westinghouse High School football team, defending city champions, are shown above. Left to right, front row: Elmer Goodson, end; Larry Malone, tackle; Charles Harris, tackle; Robert Harrison, co-captain and guard; Dave Young, center; Arthur Davis, co-captain and guard, and McKinley Broadus, end.  Back row: John Brewer, halfback; Jon Henderson, quarterback; George Webb, fullback, and Melvin Myricks, halfback. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of Westinghouse High School football team, front row from left: Elmer Goodson, Larry Malone, Charles Harris, Robert Harrison, Dave Young, Arthur Davis, McKinley Broadus; back row: John Brewer Jr., Jon Henderson, George Webb, and Melvin Myricks, gathered in formation on field
